com.aurel.track.fieldType.runtime.bl

Class CustomSelectUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aurel.track.fieldType.runtime.bl.CustomSelectUtil

  • public class CustomSelectUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class for custom selects to get the selected values as Integer[] The custom selects are considered multiple selects (@see CustomSelectBaseRT#isMultiple()), so they are loaded as Object[] (@see CustomOnePieceBaseRT#loadAttribute()) even if at renderer level they are single selects
